There is created and established within the Finance and Administration Cabinet a Kentucky Local Correctional Facilities Construction Authority, composed of ten (10) members who shall be:
The secretary of the Finance and Administration Cabinet, or his designee;
The commissioner of the Department of Corrections, or his designee;
The designee of the Kentucky Jailers Association;
The designee of the Kentucky County Judges/Executive Association;
The designee of the Kentucky Association of Counties;
The designee of the Kentucky Magistrates and Commissioners Association;
Two (2) citizen members appointed by the Governor; and
Two (2) members of the General Assembly appointed by the Governor.
